    <item>
      <title>Version 1.5</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>PastScreen 1.5 - Apple-first refinements</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Native Shortcuts:</strong> New App Intents let you trigger captures via Siri, Shortcuts or Automations.</li>
          <li><strong>Modern UI polish:</strong> Refined selection overlay, TipKit onboarding hints and improved Dock/menubar sync.</li>
          <li><strong>Notifications:</strong> Fully native UN notifications with Finder reveal, silent banner, and reliable clipboard copy.</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
